### Activation

Say **"얘들아 부탁해"** (or **"team assemble"**) to activate the full expert team system. When activated, Claude will analyze your request and automatically assign the optimal agents.

### How It Works

1. You describe what you need (in English or Korean)
2. The router detects request type (architecture, bug, optimize, etc.)
3. The right team is assembled with the right model tiers
4. Agents work through a pipeline: design → implement → test → review

