## Team Pipeline

When you say "얘들아 부탁해" (team assemble), the system:

1. **Route**: Analyzes your request to detect type (architecture, bug, optimize, etc.)
2. **Assign**: Selects the optimal tool (Claude/Codex) and agents for each phase
3. **Execute**: Runs through the pipeline phases in order
4. **Verify**: Validates output at each stage before proceeding
5. **Report**: Summarizes what was done and what needs attention

### Tool Assignment Rules

| Task Type | Tool | Reason |
|-----------|------|--------|
| Architecture / Design / Planning | Claude | Deep opus reasoning |
| Parallel implementation | Codex | Multi-agent parallel execution |
| Code review / Security review | Claude | Opus-level analysis |
| Testing / QA | Codex | Parallel test execution |
| Bug analysis / Debugging | Claude | Deep causal reasoning |
| Large refactoring | Codex | Multi-file parallel changes |

